{
  "message": "Add Series dt strftime/floor/ceil/round conformance coverage\n\nAdd conformance fixtures and harness support for dt accessor operations:\n- series_dt_strftime: Format datetime as string\n- series_dt_floor: Floor datetime to frequency\n- series_dt_ceil: Ceil datetime to frequency\n- series_dt_round: Round datetime to frequency\n\nAlso fix datetime fixtures to use utf8 kind (Scalar doesn't support datetime64).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
